show.title: Gumnaam Billionaire
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/EAAXZw
show.description: After losing his memory in a murder attempt by his own wife, this billionaire falls in love again — only to be humiliated by the powerful family of the woman he loves. But when a public business event reveals his true identity as the founder of their entire empire, he returns not for revenge… but to reclaim his name!
